properties.headline: Gale Watch issued February 5 at 7:33AM EST until February 7 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...South to Southwest winds 20 to 25 kt increasing to 25 to
30 kt becoming West on Friday. Gusts up to 35 to 40 kt. Seas
gradually building to 6 to 9 feet during the period.

* WHERE...Flagler Beach to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, from 4 AM to 1 PM EST
Thursday. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 10 AM to 4 PM EST
Friday. For the Gale Watch, from Thursday afternoon through
Friday morning.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions. Remain in port, seek safe harbor, and/or
secure the vessel for possible gale conditions.
